    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We were once far off but have become near"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In the blood of the dear Son."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In His flesh abolished all the ordinances,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thus creating two as one. [Eph. 2:13, 15]"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We have access directly to the Father"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Through Christ Jesus, our Lord"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In one Spirit, whether Jew or Gentile,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Fellowship has been restored. [Eph. 2:18]"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Make the prayer that Paul had in Ephesians"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The prayer in our daily plan."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Father strengthen us with power through Your Spirit,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Deep into the inner man. [Eph. 3:16]"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord, keep spreading into every corner,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord, keep gaining each part."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We allow you to have the room within us."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Make Your home in all our heart. [Eph. 3:17]"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord, Your riches are so unsearchable."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I can never comprehend."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But with all the saints in such a corporate church life"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Your dimensions apprehend. [Eph. 3:8, 18-19]"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "By Your mercy, keep me in Your Body,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Taking the rich supply."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Through each member’s function in their measure"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "All the Body edify. [Eph. 4:16]"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Deep within You is the greatest mystery,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "One that countless men have searched."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But to us You have unveiled the revelation,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Now we see Christ and the church. [Eph. 5:32]"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord, we’re wholly for Your heart’s desire—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Make Your church sanctified."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Through the washing in the pure word’s water"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "May You gain Your glorious Bride. [Eph. 5:25-26]"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "5"
    }
